<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-ng-app="canvas">
<head>
  %= include 'header.inc', title => 'Korora Project'
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page-container">

    %= include 'website/navigation.inc', active => 'support'

    <div class="page-content">
      <!-- CONTENT -->

      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-12">
            <h1 class="page-title"><strong>Registered.</strong> Join the Community</h1>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <h2>Your Korora Prime account is almost ready.</h2>
            <p>A message has been sent to the email address you provided with further instructions on how to finalise the activation of your account.</p>
            <a href="<%= $rt_url %>" class="btn btn-success">Return</a>
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-success">Home</a>
          </div>

          <div class="col-sm-6 callout">
            <h2>Benefits of Korora Prime.</h2>
            <p>The Korora Project are aspiring to provide the best out of the box experience for new users through to power users and experts.</p>
            <p>Right now, your Korora Prime account provides access to participate with the community via <a href="/support/engage">Engage</a>.</p>
            <p>Down the road, your Korora Prime account will provide single sign-on access to other Korora Project services that you choose to be part of.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>


      <!-- END CONTENT -->
    </div>
  </div>

  %= include 'website/footer.inc'

  <!-- MODALS -->
  %= include 'authenticate.inc'

  <!-- SCRIPTS -->
  %= include 'scripts.inc'
</body>
</html>
